{"type":"message","id":"5aed8aa8","parentId":"bd718bcc","timestamp":"2026-05-19T02:30:56.580Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to add two sub-items to the CCG玩法 template:\n1. 客户端 (Client) - default owner: 叶枝君\n2. 服务端 - default owner: 胡新雷\n\nI need to figure out the type IDs for 客户端 and 服务端. From the 1V1 template memory:\n- 客户端: typeId `1131253609001000012` (from MEMORY.md: `[12]客户端`)\n- 服务端: already exists at index [9] with typeId `1131253609001000043` (ServerStory)\n\n\nThese are TAPD template settings that need to be configured server-side, so I'll need to make the API calls to update the template configuration directly. I can see from the template configuration that I need to enable only the 客户端, 策划, and QA work item types for this template. Let me navigate to the template edit page using Playwright and make those adjustments directly in TAPD.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好，需要在 TAPD 后台编辑这个模板，增加/修改预设子工作项。先用 Playwright 找到模板编辑入口。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_vrtx_01ESDBgvugHq1VmQWLecPy6R","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"node -e \"\nconst { chromium } = require('playwright');\nconst fs = require('fs');\n(async () => {\n  const cookies = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync('tapd_cookies.json', 'utf8'));\n  const browser = await chromium.launch({ headless: false });\n  const context = await browser.newContext();\n  await context.addCookies(cookies);\n  const page = await context.newPage();\n  \n  // 尝试进入模板管理页\n  await page.goto('https://www.tapd.cn/31253609/prong/workitem_type_templates/index');\n  await page.waitForLoadState('networkidle');\n  await page.screenshot({ path: 'tapd_template_mgmt.png', fullPage: true });\n  console.log('URL:', page.url());\n  console.log('Title:', await page.title());\n  \n  // 找CCG玩法模板的链接\n  const links = await page.evaluate(() => {\n    const results = [];\n    document.querySelectorAll('a').forEach(a => {\n      if (a.textContent?.includes('CCG') || a.textContent?.includes('玩法') || a.href?.includes('1131253609001000049')) {\n        results.push({ text: a.textContent?.trim(), href: a.href });\n      }\n    });\n    return results;\n  });\n  console.log('Related links:', JSON.stringify(links));\n  await browser.close();\n})();\n\"","workdir":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace","timeout":20000}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openai-proxy","model":"giant-claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779157835715,"responseId":"chatcmpl-34fdd52c-0e25-4186-8c98-30241f8c5be3"}}
