{"type":"message","id":"ed77f51d","parentId":"7b599f8b","timestamp":"2026-05-19T02:42:19.261Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"没有模板管理入口。回到最核心的问题：TAPD dialog 里的「提交」实际上是把 treeData 写入主页面 hidden input，然后**随需求单一起提交时才保存到模板**。但等等——我重新理解一下：这个 dialog 的提交应该是**保存模板预设**，只是我没有触发到正确的接口。\n\n让我看看 JS 源码里 `j-modify-preset-stories` 真正绑定的逻辑："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_vrtx_01PBG6GNUtTnQ1UzJJawyKpf","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\find_modify_handler.mjs","content":"import { readFileSync } from 'fs';\nconst js = readFileSync('preset_helper2.js', 'utf8');\n\n// 找 modify-preset-stories 前后 5000 字符\nconst idx = js.indexOf('modify-preset-stories');\nconsole.log('Found at index:', idx);\nconst section = js.substring(Math.max(0, idx - 3000), idx + 5000);\n\n// 找 ajax/url 调用\nconst lines = section.split(';');\nfor (const line of lines) {\n  if (line.includes('url') || line.includes('ajax') || line.includes('post') || line.includes('fetch') || line.includes('$.') || line.includes('save') || line.includes('update')) {\n    console.log('>> ', line.trim().substring(0, 300));\n  }\n}\nconsole.log('\\n\\n=== Full section ===');\nconsole.log(section.substring(0, 8000));\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openai-proxy","model":"giant-claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779158528618,"responseId":"chatcmpl-69af46a8-cce1-4846-9c10-07e0ca061e07"}}
