{"type":"message","id":"dd5e96c0","parentId":"2625310e","timestamp":"2026-05-19T02:42:39.532Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"关键发现！代码里有 `_(\".j-preset-stories-head__add\").click(function(){e.addRootPresetWorkitem(),...})` 说明存在添加按钮，只是在这个 dialog 里被隐藏了。而且 `disableWorkitemTypeSelect:true` 确认了类型是锁死的。\n\n另外看到 `window.template_id` 和 `data[PresetItems]` 的 hidden input。点击提交后，数据写入主页面的 hidden input，是在**模板管理页**而不是新建需求页。\n\n让我找模板管理的真正入口："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_vrtx_01RHFsGaRwPrXCt3oqGL4j68","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"node -e \"\nconst { chromium } = require('playwright');\nconst fs = require('fs');\n(async () => {\n  const cookies = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync('tapd_cookies.json', 'utf8'));\n  const browser = await chromium.launch({ headless: false });\n  const context = await browser.newContext();\n  await context.addCookies(cookies);\n  const page = await context.newPage();\n  \n  // 尝试直接访问模板编辑页\n  const testUrls = [\n    'https://www.tapd.cn/31253609/prong/workitem_template/edit/1131253609001000047',\n    'https://www.tapd.cn/31253609/prong/workitem_template/template_list',\n    'https://www.tapd.cn/31253609/prong/workitem_types/index',\n    'https://www.tapd.cn/31253609/agile_setting/index',\n    'https://www.tapd.cn/31253609/prong/workitem_template/workitem_type_setting?workspace_id=31253609',\n  ];\n  \n  for (const url of testUrls) {\n    await page.goto(url);\n    await page.waitForLoadState('networkidle');\n    await page.waitForTimeout(1000);\n    const title = await page.title();\n    const body = (await page.evaluate(() => document.body?.innerText?.substring(0, 60)?.replace(/\\n/g, ' ')));\n    const notFound = body?.includes('不存在');\n    console.log(notFound ? '❌' : '✅', url.split('/').slice(-3).join('/'), '|', title);\n  }\n  await browser.close();\n})();\n\"","workdir":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace","timeout":25000}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openai-proxy","model":"giant-claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779158545087,"responseId":"chatcmpl-3b767ec3-212e-4160-98f1-9f5f1dee4921"}}
